      "item": "Language",
      "reviewed": false,
      "intent": "Enumerate all built-in tree-sitter languages for tree_path operations: Bash, Dart, Rust, Ruby, Python, Go, JavaScript, TypeScript, TSX, C, C++, Java, C#, PHP, Objective-C, Kotlin, Swift, and Zig. Each variant maps to a static LanguageConfig via config().",
